---
layout: layout.njk
title: Blog | Blue Quill Studio
description: Latest articles from Blue Quill Studio.
permalink: /blog/
---
<section><h1 class="section-title">Blog</h1><p class="section-sub">Latest articles on books, writing, leadership and technology.</p><div class="grid3">{% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}<a class="card post-card" href="{{ post.url }}"><p class="post-meta">{{ post.data.date }}</p><h2 class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2><p class="post-summary">{{ post.data.description }}</p><span class="btn">Read More</span></a>{% endfor %}</div></section>
